{"tid":1561173,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打絲打特別期待今年既中秋節 香港人好似一家人過中秋咁","createTime":"2019-09-11T13:32:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T16:40:15.000Z","uid":92002,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f3857319a663e8cf807775fdeb1ccfaa6c345e89","tid":1561173,"uid":92002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:32:37.000Z","msg":"雖然呢三個月黎香港發生左好多唔開心既事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但唔知點解今年對中秋節特別期待<br />\n呢一種感覺除左仲係天真無邪果陣 期待玩燈籠食月餅 已經消失左十幾年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年中秋討論既唔再係邊一隻月餅多大陸人炒<br />\n而係討論邊一隻月餅有屬於真香港人既人情味<br />\n<br />\n就算毒撚自己一個冇朋友都好 唔似往年匿埋係屋企<br />\n今年有好多社區活動 行落就有好多街坊陪你一齊過<br />\n<br />\n今年既一家人齊齊整整過中秋 唔係屬於自己屋企<br />\n而係一班齊上齊落既香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63f4ca650e21e7dd40f2b1e264866c2383c019fc","tid":1561173,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:33:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"c93a6fb4611939d42a8135765b03e625b4f8a97a","tid":1561173,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:33:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https